{"tid":777203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好憎隔離屋食煙","createTime":"2018-08-12T16:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T16:50:11.000Z","uid":166570,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f41144196216456a94295d567521d61be978ea","tid":777203,"uid":166570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:50:11.000Z","msg":"真係好討厭鄰居食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廳個窗L形咁對住，佢一煲煙，我就要關晒窗。<br />\n<br />\n廁所廚房又係<br />\n一入廁所成陣煙味，唔講仲以為自己食煙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好心啲煙咁貴就唔好浪費，吸晒入個肺到先，個窗唔好開咁大，飄晒去人地到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係避到避唔到，搬左兩次屋都咁岩隔屋係食煙既...上一次仲要係左右夾攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解啲人咁唔自愛，戒煙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}